Welcome to the Game TEXTVENTURE
-----------------------------------------
Story:
Embark on a daring mission as a skilled military pilot patrolling the skies.
Just when you thought you were in control, chaos strikes.
A colossal storm engulfs your aircraft, painting the sky with frenzied lights.
In the blink of an eye, your systems falter, leaving you no choice but to eject into the tumultuous unknown.
As you plummet towards the earth, your once-trusted plane erupts into a fiery explosion, casting you into unconsciousness.